      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ELUSIVE CURL (8) hit the ground running last time with a fast early split and never headed, leading throughout to win by 6 lengths (29.34) over 515m at this track. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. Makes plenty of appeal if runs up to latest. PAW VORTEX (2) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (23.24) at Horsham behind Paw Palmer in a Mix 3/4. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Expected to be in this for a long way. REAPER (4) clocked a superb 28.46 when winning over 510m at Sale last start. Harder here but expected to feature again. CHEEKY CHOMPERS (1) is worth some thought after placing last start.",
